{"tid":2114283,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"真男人要止汗香體  到底用咩好","createTime":"2020-07-18T16:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T13:24:33.000Z","uid":171094,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"0506233bd7f9ab83e04e547422f72d9b177074dc","tid":2114283,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一到夏天又出大汗<br />\n成日落街行幾步就成個背脊濕撚晒<br />\n用過好多款沖涼啊止汗啊都冇用<br />\n成日俾女朋友話有味<br />\n噴香水女朋友又話加埋汗味仲臭<br />\n唔想再臭親佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇巴絲打有好介紹<br />\n有埋香體介紹就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用過jo malone同ck都cover唔到啲臭味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過用呢隻都止到一半汗<br />\n但個人會熱  同埋都係會臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTGM8HZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTGM8HZ.jpg&h=080f2c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻就止到胳肋底<br />\n但搽背脊膊頭嗰啲就完全冇功效<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ANGhvWJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FANGhvWJ.jpg&h=35b61103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n噴嗰啲基本上誠哥有賣嘅男裝都用過晒<br />\n冇隻work <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8b820461b827da950d118a7ac0e3a41c5886c6","tid":2114283,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb06126f2fb9befeed23dfc5b51784456b2003d","tid":2114283,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T16:46:16.000Z","msg":"依啲愈搽愈臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15320696748933dcc5b90be1b6f09fa233a80fc3","tid":2114283,"uid":33874,"like":8